benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: GET /1.0/kb/customFields/search/{searchKey} - Search custom fields

covered: Valid Request: Happy path GET returns 200 with matching CustomField objects.
Empty Response: No matching records returns an empty JSON array (200).
Pagination: Tests cover limit/offset usage including first/next pages and offset-beyond cases.
Audit Parameter Handling: FULL/MINIMAL/NONE audit values produce corresponding audit data levels or omissions.
Query Parameter Robustness: Unknown/extra parameters are ignored and default values are applied when missing.
Authorization: Missing and invalid tokens return 401 as expected.
Error Handling: Malformed/invalid parameter values yield 400; backend service unavailability yields 503; unsupported HTTP method yields 405.
Backward Compatibility: Legacy clients using only path parameter yield 200 with matching results.
XSS/Injection Guard: Special characters in searchKey do not reflect or execute and input is sanitized.
Unicode and Boundary Handling: Unicode characters and max-length searchKey are handled without crashes.
Performance/Concurrency: Stress tests and concurrent requests demonstrate stability and response times.
Integration/Documentation: Data consistency across integrated sources and descriptive error messages are verified.
Default Value Coverage: Default pagination and audit settings are handled correctly when not specified.
gaps: Rate Limiting: No tests covering rate limiting/throttling behavior under high load.
Caching Behavior: No tests validating ETag/Cache-Control headers or cache behavior.
Forbidden Access Scenarios: No tests for 403 responses or permission-related access control.
Internal Server Error coverage: No explicit test for 500 range errors.
recommendations: Add rate-limiting/throttling tests (e.g., 429) under simulated high load or bursts.
Add tests validating caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control) and cache behavior.
Add tests for 403 Forbidden scenarios to confirm proper handling of insufficient permissions.
Add tests for 500 Internal Server Error scenarios and error recovery.
Clarify deterministic handling for edge cases around empty searchKey and ensure explicit expectation (e.g., treat empty as invalid or as valid with empty results).
